{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"aria-orientation 属性の使用","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-orientation_attribute","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria/#aria-orientation\" rel=\"external noopener\">aria-orientation</a>&nbsp;属性は、要素が水平方向か垂直方向かを示すために使用されます。</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>語彙</p>\n\n<table style=\"width: 50%;\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>vertical</td>\n   <td>要素は垂直方向です。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>horizontal</td>\n   <td>要素は水平方向です。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>undefined（デフォルト）</td>\n   <td>要素の方向は不明または曖昧です。</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"possible_effects_on_user_agents_and_assistive_technology","title":"ユーザーエージェントと支援技術への影響","isH3":true,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><strong>注</strong>: 支援技術がこの手法をどのように扱うべきかについての意見は異なる場合があります。 上記の情報は、これらの意見の1つで、したがって規範的ではありません。</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"example_1\" name=\"Example_1\">例 1:</h4>\n\n<p>下のスニペットは、垂直方向に向けられた単純なスライダを示しています。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>handle_zoomSlider<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">role</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>slider<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-orientation</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>vertical<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-valuemin</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-valuemax</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>17<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-valuenow</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>14<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>11<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"used_with_aria_roles","title":"ARIA ロールで使用","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>scrollbar</li>\n <li>listbox</li>\n <li>combobox</li>\n <li>menu</li>\n <li>tree</li>\n <li>separator</li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/slider_role\" title=\"Using the slider role\">slider</a></li>\n <li>tablist</li>\n <li>toolbar</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"related_aria_techniques","title":"関連する ARIA 技術","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatibility","title":"互換性","isH3":true,"content":"<p class=\"comment\">TBD: 一般的な UA と AT 製品の組み合わせに関するサポート情報を追加する</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"additional_resources","title":"その他のリソース","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria/#aria-orientation\" rel=\" noopener\">aria-orientation の WAI-ARIA 仕様</a>（英語）</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"aria-orientation 属性は、要素が水平方向か垂直方向かを示すために使用されます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Utiliser l'attribut aria-orientation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/accessibility/aria/aria_techniques/using_the_aria-orientation_attribute","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/accessibility/aria/aria_techniques/using_the_aria-orientation_attribute/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility","title":"アクセシビリティ"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA","title":"ARIA"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques","title":"ARIA を使用する: ロール、ステート、プロパティ"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/ARIA_Techniques/Using_the_aria-orientation_attribute","title":"aria-orientation 属性の使用"}],"pageTitle":"aria-orientation 属性の使用 - アクセシビリティ | MDN","noIndexing":false}}